      • elemDivision

        public ModuloMath elemDivision(int number,
                               int divisor)
        Description of elemDivision(int number1, int number2)
        Parameters:
        number - int - First Number
        divisor - int - Divisor
        Returns:
        ModuloMath number1 MODULO number2 (remainder of number1/number2) ALGORITHM
        1. Compute number / divisor and store in result
        2. Compute number % divisor and store in remainder
        3. Create a new ModuleMath class initializing it with result and divisor
        4. Return the ModuleMath instance created in (3).
